<section id="what-gets-captured-per-run" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="what-gets-captured-per-run">What Gets Captured Per Run</h3>
<p>After every pipeline run, <code>nf-prov</code> writes an <code>ro-crate-metadata.json</code> into your output directory that records:</p>
<ul>
<li>Workflow version (exact git commit or tag)</li>
<li>Input files with checksums (MD5/SHA256)</li>
<li>Output files with checksums and sizes</li>
<li>Start and end timestamps per process</li>
<li>Container image IDs used per process</li>
<li>Full resolved parameter set at runtime</li>
</ul>
